markets.title: Will Ivanka Trump speak at Trump's second inauguration ceremony?
markets.rules_primary: If Ivanka Trump speaks during the second inauguration ceremony for Donald Trump, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: This applies to those speaking to the crowd during and before the inauguration of the President, and does not include informal remarks or parts of the inauguration other than the ceremony (typically held on the Capitol balcony) itself. Examples include persons delivering an invocation, singing, reading a poem, or giving a speech.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
